":"Когда Thomas Proude родился в 1481 г. в местности валтам, кэнт, Англия, Великобритания, его отцу по имени Wilhelmus Proude было 26 лет, а матери, которую звали Wife of Wilhelmus Proude, 22. У него был по крайней мере 1 сын от Proude. Он умер 8 сентября 1545 г. в его родном городе в возрасте 64 лет и был похоронен в местности сэндвич, кэнт, Англия, Великобритания."},"sm":{"1481–8 September 1545":"1481–8 Setema 1545","1481–1545":"1481–1545","1481–Male":"1481–Ua Maliu","1486–Female":"1486–Ua Maliu","1507–1545":"1507–1545","1455–Male":"1455–Ua Maliu","1459–Female":"1459–Ua Maliu","1459":"1459","1545":"1545","1455":"1455","1486":"1486","20 September 1558":"20 Setema 1558","1481":"1481","1507":"1507","1480":"1480","8 September 1545":"8 Setema 1545","St Mary The Virgin's Church, Sandwich St Peter, Sandwich, Kent, England, United Kingdom":"Sandwich, Kent, Egelani, United Kingdom","Waltham, Kent, England, United Kingdom":"Waltham, Kent, Egelani, United Kingdom","Canterbury, Kent, England, United Kingdom":"Canterbury, Kent, Egelani, United Kingdom","Of Canterbury, Kent, England":"Canterbury, Kent, Egelani"},"sk":{"1481–8 September 1545":"1481–8. september 1545","1481–1545":"1481–1545","1481–Male":"1481–Zosnulý","1486–Female":"1486–Zosnulá","1507–1545":"1507–1545","1455–Male":"1455–Zosnulý","1459–Female":"1459–Zosnulá","1459":"1459","1545":"1545","1455":"1455","1486":"1486","20 September 1558":"20. september 1558","1481":"1481","1507":"1507","1480":"1480","8 September 1545":"8. september 1545","St Mary The Virgin's Church, Sandwich St Peter, Sandwich, Kent, England, United Kingdom":"Sandwich, Kent, Anglicko, Spojené kráľovstvo","Waltham, Kent, England, United Kingdom":"Waltham, Kent, Anglicko, Spojené kráľovstvo","Canterbury, Kent, England, United Kingdom":"Canterbury, Kent, Anglicko, Spojené kráľovstvo","Of Canterbury, Kent, England":"Canterbury, Kent, England"},"es":{"1481–8 September 1545":"1481–8 de septiembre de 1545","1481–1545":"1481–1545","1481–Male":"1481–Fallecido